Reasoning: The paper proposes a new graphical technique for representing relations between an agent's sensorimotor loop and an adaptive internal model. This technique has applications in developmental models and related fields. Given these factors, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper deals with modeling and learning. The sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.RO (Robotics) are also likely, as the paper deals with sensorimotor loops and their relation to internal models, which are relevant to these fields. Finally, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible sub-category, as the paper deals with the control of sensorimotor systems.
